    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-01-29T21:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-01-29T21:00:00-05:00" n="130"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d130">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/3711: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul General at Shanghai (<persName corresp="#p_CES1"
                            type="from">Cunningham</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Shanghai</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-01-30T10:00:00+08:00"
                            >January 30, 1932—10 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received January 30—1 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Following to the Legation: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>Your January 29, 3 p.m.,<note n="83" xml:id="d130fn83">See telegram No.
                                148, January 29, 5 p.m., to the Department from the Minister in
                                China, <ref target="#pg_97">p. 97</ref>.</note> last paragraph.
                            Suggestion made by Japanese staff officer to Secretary General of
                            Council reported in my telegram of January 28, 2 p.m. is not favorably
                            considered by Council. I shall, however, carry out Legation’s
                            instructions.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_CES1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Cunningham</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
